causing a miscarriage.

32:37.738 --> 32:39.174
So Blake's been
acting from

32:39.218 --> 32:41.176
a sense of pain that neither one
of us can comprehend.

32:41.220 --> 32:43.004
I understand.

32:43.048 --> 32:46.703
It's still a big step to murder,

32:46.747 --> 32:49.010
just maybe not a giant leap.

32:49.054 --> 32:50.403
He's still our father.

32:50.446 --> 32:52.318
And it's not like you've
never forgiven him before.

32:52.361 --> 32:55.190
And you got to live in
the manor your whole life.

32:55.234 --> 32:58.237
So why is it so bad for me
to want the same thing?

33:01.153 --> 33:02.676
You guys sure do walk slow.

33:02.719 --> 33:05.548
Kirby? What are
you doing here?

33:05.592 --> 33:07.028
You told me to make
my own decisions.

33:07.072 --> 33:08.725
That means Joel doesn't
get to make them either.

33:08.769 --> 33:10.031
So I, uh,

33:10.075 --> 33:11.206
stole his phone
and called my dad,

33:11.250 --> 33:12.381
and he'll be here
in a few minutes.

33:12.425 --> 33:13.992
From the manor? How?

33:14.035 --> 33:15.645
He put a tracker on your phone
or something, I don't know.

33:15.689 --> 33:17.299
He left the manor
a few hours ago.

33:19.171 --> 33:21.129
So, do you want a ride home?

33:21.173 --> 33:22.261
Oh, please.
Yes, I feel like

33:22.304 --> 33:24.350
this burlap sack
is giving me hives.

33:24.393 --> 33:26.569
Okay, cool.

33:26.613 --> 33:27.744
Here you go.

33:27.788 --> 33:29.050
Thank you.

33:42.585 --> 33:45.588
Alexis! Stop!

33:45.632 --> 33:46.894
I just want to talk.

33:46.937 --> 33:48.243
Yesterday you
kicked me out.

33:48.287 --> 33:49.636
Now you won't
let me leave.

33:49.679 --> 33:51.290
I'm starting
to worry about you.

33:51.333 --> 33:53.770
They say the mind is the first
thing to go, but in your case,

33:53.814 --> 33:54.815
it might be
the third thing,

33:54.858 --> 33:57.252
after taste in men
and fashion sense.

33:57.296 --> 33:58.775
Now that I know
that it wasn't Mack

33:58.819 --> 34:00.255
who fired the bullet
that killed Mark,

34:00.299 --> 34:02.083
and it certainly
wasn't a hunter

34:02.127 --> 34:04.955
on our property,
I wonder: who did?

34:04.999 --> 34:06.783
What are you blathering on
about now?

34:06.827 --> 34:09.221
You lied to sneak into
the manor yesterday.

34:09.264 --> 34:10.570
You lied to
get in today.

34:10.613 --> 34:13.312
But worse, you lied about
seeing Mack on a day

34:13.355 --> 34:14.443
he wasn't even in town.

34:14.487 --> 34:18.969
