♪ 'Cause I don't wanna go...

34:24.932 --> 34:28.892
Well, now we both know I don't
need to since I have this.

34:28.936 --> 34:31.025
Who doesn't carry in this state?

34:31.069 --> 34:32.766
It was you.

34:32.809 --> 34:34.420
You killed Mark.

34:34.463 --> 34:37.292
I was aiming for you, you bitch.

34:38.511 --> 34:39.816
And I am sorry I missed.

34:44.517 --> 34:47.911
♪ Tell me, tell me
what you really want from me ♪

34:47.955 --> 34:51.306
♪ You gotta let me know

34:51.350 --> 34:54.483
♪ I'm falling off
