34:59.314 --> 35:02.491
♪ Volcano girls,
we really can't be beat ♪

35:02.535 --> 35:06.147
♪ Warm us up and watch us blow

35:06.191 --> 35:09.498
♪ But now and then we fail
and we admit defeat ♪

35:09.542 --> 35:11.283
♪ We're falling off

