To life!OTHERS: To life!

35:31.085 --> 35:32.826
Drowning you
in this pond

35:32.869 --> 35:34.871
would be the justice
you deserve,

35:34.915 --> 35:36.221
you bottom-feeding bitch.

35:37.657 --> 35:41.008
But it won't bring back Mark
or my baby.

35:42.531 --> 35:44.490
You'll get what's coming to you.

35:44.533 --> 35:46.883
I'll make sure of it.

35:46.927 --> 35:48.537
Good luck.

35:48.581 --> 35:50.844
Try to pin
this murder on me,

35:50.887 --> 35:53.716
it'll just expose the fact
that Blake killed Mack.

35:53.760 --> 35:54.978
♪ 'Cause I don't wanna go...

