36:17.566 --> 36:20.090
Because, unlike you,
they're real people...

36:20.134 --> 36:22.180
Well, damn, Thor.

36:22.223 --> 36:23.920
Way to drop the hammer.
Insulting the reps

36:23.964 --> 36:26.401
wouldn't have been
my first move, but you're lucky

36:26.445 --> 36:29.099
everyone's loving the video's
anti-corporate vibe.

36:29.143 --> 36:31.232
Fan buy-ins are pouring in.

36:31.276 --> 36:33.930
Season ticket requests
are blowing up,

36:33.974 --> 36:35.802
because people want
to see their team

36:35.845 --> 36:38.239
with their name
somewhere on the stadium.

36:38.283 --> 36:41.242
AXFC ain't going nowhere.

36:41.286 --> 36:42.939
That sounds like the mindset
of a owner

36:42.983 --> 36:44.419
who's here
for the right reasons.

36:44.463 --> 36:45.768
And to be clear,

36:45.812 --> 36:47.422
that wasn't luck.

36:47.466 --> 36:48.684
Who do you think

36:48.728 --> 36:49.816
shot that video,

36:49.859 --> 36:51.948
then leaked it
into the right hands?

36:51.992 --> 36:54.386
That was you?With a little help
from my friends.

36:54.429 --> 36:56.126
SAM:
I got to say,

36:56.170 --> 36:57.867
I may have a career
in filmmaking.

36:57.911 --> 36:59.695
Did you notice
how sometimes I drop the angle,

36:59.739 --> 37:01.349
like I'm not trying to record?

37:01.393 --> 37:03.264
You're the Tarantino
of Internet videos.

37:03.308 --> 37:05.919
With your eye, Culhane's
message, my contacts,

37:05.962 --> 37:08.791
we turned this Hail Mary pass
into a viral touchdown.

37:08.835 --> 37:11.794
Uh, we're totally...

37:11.838 --> 37:13.274
a dream team.

37:13.318 --> 37:16.799
Um, a dream team
that wasn't real.

37:16.843 --> 37:18.323
We were role-playing.

37:18.366 --> 37:19.802
And not in the fun way.

37:19.846 --> 37:21.848
Look, if you want
to be with me,

37:21.891 --> 37:23.241
I'm gonna need you
to give me more.

37:24.807 --> 37:26.156
Of you.

37:29.682 --> 37:30.683
Okay.

37:32.162 --> 37:33.468
Baylor.

37:37.037 --> 37:38.821
It's Sam.

37:38.865 --> 37:39.953
My middle name,

37:39.996 --> 37:41.781
it's... Baylor.

37:44.087 --> 37:46.351
I'm sorry I've
been holding back.

37:46.394 --> 37:49.049
I promise I'll be better.

37:50.050 --> 37:51.443
Baylor?

37:51.486 --> 37:52.879
Really?

37:52.922 --> 37:54.881
Did your parents
not like you?

37:54.924 --> 37:56.665
FALLON:
A promise is a promise.

37:56.709 --> 37:58.363
And I am a woman
of my word,

37:58.406 --> 38:00.103
so I will go talk
to Blake for you.

38:00.147 --> 38:01.714
Now, I can't promise
that it'll help,

38:01.757 --> 38:03.977
because, at the end of the day,
he's still Blake,

38:04.020 --> 38:06.109
so I wouldn't give up
your secret loft just yet.

38:06.153 --> 38:07.546
Hey. Don't bother.

38:07.589 --> 38:09.417
He's either going to forgive me
or he's not.

38:09.461 --> 38:11.027
Nothing you say is gonna matter.

38:11.071 --> 38:15.075
And that's not the reason I
went on this little adventure.

38:15.118 --> 38:16.337
Then why do it?

38:16.381 --> 38:17.773
So you could stand next to Joel

38:17.817 --> 38:19.471
to make yourself
seem less insane?

38:20.602 --> 38:22.082
No, it was still about family,

38:22.125 --> 38:23.518
just not about Father.

38:23.562 --> 38:25.477
I thought this would be
a great opportunity

38:25.520 --> 38:27.957
to get away from all this and...

38:28.001 --> 38:30.090
really get to know my sister.

38:35.138 --> 38:36.836
And my wife.

38:36.879 --> 38:40.143
You just had to do it.

38:42.755 --> 38:45.061
Hey. Um,

38:45.105 --> 38:47.412
I just wanted to say thanks
again for coming today.

38:47.455 --> 38:51.111
Even though I didn't really
need you to.

38:51.154 --> 38:52.547
Yeah. I know that now.

38:52.591 --> 38:53.679
I'm just relieved

38:53.722 --> 38:55.202
that you decided, on your own,

38:55.245 --> 38:56.595
to come home.

38:56.638 --> 38:59.206
Well, you might have
majorly embarrassed yourself

38:59.249 --> 39:01.600
along the way, but I think
you've grown a bit, too.

39:01.643 --> 39:03.602
Yeah, I doubt that.

39:03.645 --> 39:06.779
Growth isn't really my thing.

39:12.175 --> 39:13.438
Fallon?

39:13.481 --> 39:14.656
Everything okay?

39:15.657 --> 39:17.485
Yeah.

39:17.529 --> 39:19.487
Yeah, I'm just...

39:19.531 --> 39:22.055
worried you may be right.

39:22.098 --> 39:24.318
Maybe growth ismy thing.

