FALLON:
I wanted to write
to say I'm sorry.

39:39.855 --> 39:43.729
About Mack
and Cristal and your baby.

39:43.772 --> 39:46.471
I know the full story.

39:46.514 --> 39:48.168
It doesn't excuse your actions,

39:48.211 --> 39:50.605
but you could have at least
told me, so I could have tried

39:50.649 --> 39:52.346
to understand
why you did what you did,

39:52.390 --> 39:55.349
but clearly you don't trust me.

39:55.393 --> 39:57.003
You're just willing to use me

39:57.046 --> 39:59.397
like you use everyone else
in your life.

39:59.440 --> 40:02.356
But thanks
to a few crazy people,

40:02.400 --> 40:04.489
I was forced to look
in the mirror.

40:04.532 --> 40:06.360
I know now
that I need to own up

40:06.404 --> 40:08.928
to my part
in our troubled relationship,

40:08.971 --> 40:11.757
but I can't keep forgiving you
for everything.

40:11.800 --> 40:15.761
I am done enabling
your self-serving behavior,

40:15.804 --> 40:18.764
but I am also done
blaming you for mine.

